{# ── Intro ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
<section class="researcher-intro">
  <div class="researcher-intro-inner">
    <p class="researcher-intro-text">
      Generation AI is a multidisciplinary research project producing scientific knowledge on AI education, children's rights in algorithmic environments and digital inequality. The project is funded by the Academy of Finland's Strategic Research Council SHIELD programme.
    </p>
    <div class="researcher-intro-actions">
      <a class="researcher-intro-btn researcher-intro-btn--primary" href="#publications">Scientific publications</a>
      <a class="researcher-intro-btn researcher-intro-btn--secondary" href="/en/shield-programme/">SHIELD programme</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── Research themes ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
<section class="researcher-themes">
  <div class="researcher-themes-inner">
    <h2 class="researcher-themes-heading">Research Agenda</h2>
    <p class="researcher-themes-lead">The project covers four interconnected research themes.</p>
    <div class="researcher-themes-grid">

      <div class="researcher-theme-card">
        <div class="researcher-theme-num">01</div>
        <h3 class="researcher-theme-title">Pedagogical models for AI education</h3>
        <p class="researcher-theme-desc">We develop and evaluate new teaching tools and methods for pre-primary and primary education. The aim is practical pedagogy that does not require coding skills.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="researcher-theme-card">
        <div class="researcher-theme-num">02</div>
        <h3 class="researcher-theme-title">Children's rights in AI systems</h3>
        <p class="researcher-theme-desc">We study children's consent, privacy and decision-making capacity in AI-based learning environments in relation to the UN Convention on the Rights of the Child and the EU General Data Protection Regulation.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="researcher-theme-card">
        <div class="researcher-theme-num">03</div>
        <h3 class="researcher-theme-title">Cybersecurity and the algorithmic environment</h3>
        <p class="researcher-theme-desc">We investigate how the algorithmic environment — recommendation systems, profiling, disinformation — affects children's and young people's sense of safety and trust.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="researcher-theme-card">
        <div class="researcher-theme-num">04</div>
        <h3 class="researcher-theme-title">Digital inequality and agency</h3>
        <p class="researcher-theme-desc">We examine skills gaps and digital agency: who benefits from AI and who is left behind — and how educational solutions can narrow these divides.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

